# Database Schema & DTOs

## PostgreSQL Tables (Neon + pgvector)

### users

Stores GitHub OAuth-authenticated dashboard users.

```sql
id                      UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
github_id               BIGINT UNIQUE NOT NULL
login                   VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
email                   VARCHAR(255)
avatar_url              VARCHAR(512)
access_token_encrypted  TEXT                         -- AES-256 encrypted
created_at              TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
updated_at              TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
```

### github_installations

One row per GitHub App installation (org or personal account).

```sql
id                        UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
installation_id           BIGINT UNIQUE NOT NULL     -- GitHub's installation ID
account_login             VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
account_type              VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL        -- 'org' | 'user'
account_avatar_url        VARCHAR(512)
access_token_encrypted    TEXT                        -- cached installation token (encrypted)
access_token_expires_at   TIMESTAMPTZ
created_at                TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
updated_at                TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
```

### repositories

Repos with the GitHub App installed; each repo belongs to one installation.

```sql
id               UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
github_id        BIGINT UNIQUE NOT NULL
installation_id  UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES github_installations(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
owner            VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
name             VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
full_name        VARCHAR(512) NOT NULL               -- "owner/name"
default_branch   VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'main'
is_active        BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true       -- review on/off per repo
language         VARCHAR(100)                        -- primary language (nullable)
created_at       TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
updated_at       TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
```

### agent_configs

Per-repo agent toggles. 1:1 with repositories; created automatically on install.

```sql
id                UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
repository_id     UUID UNIQUE NOT NULL REFERENCES repositories(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
security_enabled  BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true
perf_enabled      BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true
arch_enabled      BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true
test_enabled      BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true
min_severity      VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'medium'  -- minimum severity to post comment
created_at        TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
updated_at        TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
```

### review_jobs

Async job queue state. Written by webhook handler; consumed by worker.
Idempotency key: UNIQUE(repository_id, head_sha) — prevents duplicate reviews for the same commit.

```sql
id              UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
repository_id   UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES repositories(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
pr_number       INTEGER NOT NULL
pr_title        VARCHAR(512) NOT NULL
pr_author       VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
pr_url          VARCHAR(512) NOT NULL
base_sha        VARCHAR(40) NOT NULL
head_sha        VARCHAR(40) NOT NULL
status          VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'pending'  -- pending|running|completed|failed
attempt_count   INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0              -- max 3 (exponential backoff)
error_message   TEXT
enqueued_at     TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
started_at      TIMESTAMPTZ
completed_at    TIMESTAMPTZ
created_at      TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
updated_at      TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
UNIQUE(repository_id, head_sha)
```

### reviews

Completed review output. 1:1 with review_jobs.

```sql
id                 UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
job_id             UUID UNIQUE NOT NULL REFERENCES review_jobs(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
repository_id      UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES repositories(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
pr_number          INTEGER NOT NULL
head_sha           VARCHAR(40) NOT NULL
pr_url             VARCHAR(512) NOT NULL
summary            TEXT                                -- overall review summary text
total_findings     INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0
critical_count     INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0
high_count         INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0
medium_count       INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0
low_count          INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0
info_count         INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0
agents_run         JSONB NOT NULL DEFAULT '[]'         -- list[AgentType] that ran
langfuse_trace_id  VARCHAR(255)
posted_to_github   BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT false
created_at         TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
updated_at         TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
```

### findings

Individual line-level review findings. Many per review.

```sql
id                  UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
review_id           UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES reviews(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
severity            VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL        -- critical|high|medium|low|info
category            VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL        -- security|perf|arch|test
agent_source        VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL        -- which agent produced this finding
file_path           VARCHAR(512) NOT NULL
line_start          INTEGER
line_end            INTEGER
title               VARCHAR(512) NOT NULL
description         TEXT NOT NULL
fix_suggestion      TEXT
github_comment_id   BIGINT                      -- set after posting to GitHub
created_at          TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
```

### code_embeddings

Chunked file embeddings for RAG context retrieval (pgvector extension required).

```sql
id               UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
repository_id    UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES repositories(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
commit_sha       VARCHAR(40) NOT NULL
file_path        VARCHAR(512) NOT NULL
chunk_index      INTEGER NOT NULL
content          TEXT NOT NULL
embedding        VECTOR(768)                    -- Gemini text-embedding-004 (768 dims)
node_type        VARCHAR(100)                   -- function|class|module (from tree-sitter)
node_name        VARCHAR(255)
language         VARCHAR(100)
created_at       TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
UNIQUE(repository_id, commit_sha, file_path, chunk_index)
```

