## Pydantic v2 DTOs

### Auth

```python
# GET /api/v1/auth/callback response
class UserDTO(BaseModel):
    id: UUID
    github_id: int
    login: str
    avatar_url: str | None

class AuthTokenDTO(BaseModel):
    access_token: str
    token_type: Literal["bearer"] = "bearer"
    user: UserDTO
```

### Repositories

```python
# GET /api/v1/repos/{id}/config  GET + PATCH
class AgentConfigDTO(BaseModel):
    repository_id: UUID
    security_enabled: bool
    perf_enabled: bool
    arch_enabled: bool
    test_enabled: bool
    min_severity: str                          # Severity enum value

class UpdateAgentConfigRequest(BaseModel):     # PATCH body — all fields optional
    security_enabled: bool | None = None
    perf_enabled: bool | None = None
    arch_enabled: bool | None = None
    test_enabled: bool | None = None
    min_severity: str | None = None

class RepoDTO(BaseModel):
    id: UUID
    github_id: int
    full_name: str
    default_branch: str
    is_active: bool
    language: str | None
    agent_config: AgentConfigDTO               # always embedded
```

